 ministration of judgment came. The desolation of Sodom </div><div class="t m5f x44 hc y201 ff3 fs5 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and Gomorrah is a perpetual reminder of the certainty of God&apos;s judgment </div><div class="t m276 x44 hc y7fb ff3 fs5 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">upon sin. </div><div class="t m5f6 x1c hd y7be ff5 fs5 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">55 </div><div class="t m5f7 xd h47 y7fc ff2 fs27 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
